Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The identity of the Titans who have been destroying the walls is revealed, but has their treachery been discovered too late to save humanity?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 11
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: A middle-school student is framed for the murder of his classmates and he is sentenced to a prison that doubles as a demented theme park in this new series.
Title: DEADMAN WONDERLAND, VOL. 1
Author: Jinsei Katoka and Kazuma Kondou
Contributor: by Jinsei Katoka and Kazuma Kondou

Description: In this latest volume, Naruto stands up to Tobi and the Allied Shinobi Forces battle the Ten-Tailed Beast.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 64
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, the Titans attack, but one of them goes rogue.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 2
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father's rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 1
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: Tomoe reveals that he is dying from a 500-year-old curse. Will Nanami be able to save him?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 14
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, what happens when a human boy becomes a Titan?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 3
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Neyn sends a team of vampire slayers to kill Staz and rescue her daughter. But does Fuyumi even want to be saved?
Title: BLOOD LAD, VOL. 4
Author: Yuuki Kodama

Description: Ciel enters a college cricket tournament to earn an invitation to the exclusive "Midnight Tea Party" hosted by the school's headmaster.
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 16
Author: Yana Toboso
